<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Leonidas Kwan - Professional Resume</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #5b21b6; /* Purple - fits a trendy/fashion retail vibe */
            --dark: #1e293b;
            --light-bg: #fdfcfd;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .resume-card {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 45px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-top: 6px solid var(--primary);
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--dark);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .info {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .entry {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .entry-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .entry-sub {
            color: #7c3aed;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        ul {
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .skill-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--dark);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .skill-item span {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #475569;
        }

        @media print {
            body { background: white; padding: 0; }
            .resume-card { box-shadow: none; border: none; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="resume-card">
    <header>
        <h1>Leonidas Kwan</h1>
        <div class="info">
            Sugar Land, TX • 713-265-8569 • leokwan.sltx@gmail.com
        </div>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Objective</h2>
        <p>
            Detail-oriented and technically proficient high school senior with a strong background in <strong>hardware assembly, quality control, and customer-facing freelance work.</strong> Proven ability to troubleshoot complex systems and maintain high standards of organization. Seeking to bring a "solution-first" attitude and strong work ethic to the team at Plato's Closet.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Experience & Projects</h2>
        
        <div class="entry">
            <div class="entry-header">
                <span>Technical Freelancer / Hardware Specialist</span>
                <span>2024 – Present</span>
            </div>
            <div class="entry-sub">Custom PC & Keyboard Assembly | Web Solutions</div>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> Assembled high-value custom PCs and mechanical keyboards, requiring extreme attention to detail and part authentication.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Support:</strong> Actively troubleshoot hardware and software issues independently, resolving glitches to ensure 100% system uptime.</li>
                <li><strong>Business Operations:</strong> Developed a custom web suite for a client to automate invoicing, demonstrating a strong grasp of data entry and financial accuracy.</li>
                <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Consulted with clients to translate their visual preferences into physical builds, ensuring high customer satisfaction.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div class="entry">
            <div class="entry-header">
                <span>Kempner High School</span>
                <span>Graduation: May 2026</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info" style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0;">Sugar Land, TX</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Skills & Strengths</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
            <div class="skill-item">
                <strong>Operational Tech</strong>
                <span>Rapidly learns POS systems, inventory software, and troubleshooting hardware (printers/registers).</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
                <strong>Attention to Detail</strong>
                <span>Experienced in identifying small defects and authenticating high-quality components and brands.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
                <strong>Programming Stack</strong>
                <span>Java (Primary), Python (Certified), JavaScript, HTML/CSS.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
                <strong>Work Ethic</strong>
                <span>Independent problem-solver, punctual, and comfortable in fast-paced environments.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

</body>
</html>
